#* '''2004''', K. R. Goodearl, R. B. Warfield, Jr., ''An Introduction to Noncommutative Noetherian Rings'', 2nd Edition, {{w|Cambridge University Press}}, [https://books.google.com.au/books?id=vXh1MtvQr_8C&pg=PA47&dq=%22ideal%22%7C%22ideals%22+ring&hl=en&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjS54O5qdPdAhWL-VQKHVHvDWIQ6AEIngEwFQ#v=onepage&q=%22ideal%22%7C%22ideals%22%20ring&f=false page 47],
